{"tid":1695683,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［唔好打飛機住］建議將軍澳手足短時間唔好encore住","createTime":"2019-11-05T19:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T19:11:04.000Z","uid":280349,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a22a832ed3518876cf224c1b235031b98f3a8b65","tid":1695683,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:07:49.000Z","msg":"我估今場已經完左，最後拉左個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然無拉到好多個，但大家唔好打飛機住（今場真係好危，包抄）<br />\n今日啲狗量真係好多而打嘅人好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n罷哂啲天橋位<br />\n又無業主立案法團主席頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得個拉票議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟今場咁多狗會唔會因為佢地背後有任務（關於周同學）？定想覆桌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果今日真係無拉好多人，聽日會唔會再黎<br />\n佢地會唔會又進化左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以真係唔建議聽晚主動再聚集人<br />\n公海咁多mon po 狗，一話聚人可能又成個東九龍狗去哂等你<br />\n想幫周同學街坊圍內就靜靜地做<br />\n我唔想好似上次屯門咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同一個路數唔好黎咁多次，一定會比對家捉到<br />\n以上只係我意見<br />\n但大家再黎料我都會尊重<br />\n就算係其他區嘅開花我都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想啲狗無傷過但手足又拉左好多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔好下下開花同啲狗講你地係邊度聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aeb31dd99729ccef388c0680a815d7e396b597a","tid":1695683,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:10:19.000Z","msg":"大家認真考慮下"},{"pid":"fd966d88df9967e29ad9c56fc83b322631cf4edf","tid":1695683,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:11:04.000Z","msg":"唔該大家諗下"}]}